name: Micro DI
details:
Smart direct input box with ultra low distortion, it quietly transfers the sound of guitar or bass directly to the audio system Balanced/unbalanced output, gain switch, cabinet simulator and ground lift function included
Full metal shell
Very small and exquisite
True bypass
Requires DC 9V Adapter power supply
